citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:11-1:41pm on
11/5/2024. The inspector attempted to contact the registrant by knocking, calling and texting. After 30 minutes with no
response, the inspector left the facility. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a
serious violation of the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
